3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/paralegal-duties-and-responsibilities\/#Paralegal_duties_and_responsibilities\" title=\"Paralegal duties and responsibilities\">Paralegal duties and responsibilities<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/paralegal-duties-and-responsibilities\/#What_does_a_Paralegal_do_Paralegal_Duties_and_Responsibilities\" title=\"What does a Paralegal do?| Paralegal Duties and Responsibilities\">What does a Paralegal do?| Paralegal Duties and Responsibilities<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/paralegal-duties-and-responsibilities\/#Paralegal_skills_and_qualifications\" title=\"Paralegal skills and qualifications\">Paralegal skills and qualifications<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/paralegal-duties-and-responsibilities\/#Paralegal_salary_expectations\" title=\"Paralegal salary expectations\">Paralegal salary expectations<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/paralegal-duties-and-responsibilities\/#Paralegal_experience_requirements_Paralegal_Duties_and_Responsibilities\" title=\"Paralegal experience requirements| Paralegal Duties and Responsibilities\">Paralegal experience requirements| Paralegal Duties and Responsibilities<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Paralegals have duties and Responsibilities to carryout, learn how to become a successful paralegal in this article.<\/span><br \/>\n<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2317 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/paralegal-lead-pic-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"Paralegal Duties and Responsibilities\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong>Paralegal duties and responsibilities<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #993300;\" href=\"#_Toc83610274\">What does a Paralegal do?<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #993300;\" href=\"#_Toc83610275\">Paralegal skills and qualifications<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #993300;\" href=\"#_Toc83610276\">Paralegal salary expectations<\/a><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83610277\"><span style=\"color: #993300;\"><strong>Paralegal experience requirements<\/strong><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"paralegal-duties-and-responsibilities\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Paralegal_duties_and_responsibilities\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83610273\"><\/a>Paralegal duties and responsibilities<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Summarizing cases and preparing reports for attorneys<\/li>\n<li>Conducting research, investigating facts and developing legal arguments<\/li>\n<li>Drafting legal documents such as contracts, depositions and pleadings<\/li>\n<li>Preparing and filing documents with courts<\/li>\n<li>Organizing and archiving the documents related to completed and ongoing cases<\/li>\n<li>Keeping track of changes in legal framework and providing timely updates on these changes<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"what-does-a-paralegal-do-paralegal-duties-and-responsibilities\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_does_a_Paralegal_do_Paralegal_Duties_and_Responsibilities\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83610274\"><\/a>What does a Paralegal do?| Paralegal Duties and Responsibilities<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2315 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/whatdoesaparalegaldo-300x240.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"240\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Paralegals sustain Attorneys in law firms by gathering, organizing and preparing a variety of credentials and files for court cases. They regularly meet with attorneys, clients or other legal professionals to get some helpful details about next gathering. Paralegals will prepare other legal credentials, like wills, contracts, briefs, appeals and pleadings.<\/p>\n<p>They\u2019ll carry out investigations to fact-check information for different cases by searching through public records and other resources provided by clients. Paralegals are also in charge of coordinating deliveries of subpoenas and other important legal credentials.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"paralegal-skills-and-qualifications\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Paralegal_skills_and_qualifications\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83610275\"><\/a>Paralegal skills and qualifications<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><strong><em>Examples of Paralegal skills and qualifications:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Certification or associate\u2019s degree in paralegal studies (bachelor\u2019s degree is preferred)<\/li>\n<li>A minimum experience of two years in a paralegal role<\/li>\n<li>Investigative mind and strong research skills<\/li>\n<li>Working knowledge legal database software<\/li>\n<li>Experience in preparing legal reports<\/li>\n<li>Excellent communication and time management skills<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"paralegal-salary-expectations\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Paralegal_salary_expectations\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83610276\"><\/a>Paralegal salary expectations<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2316 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/salary-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"Paralegal Duties and Responsibilities\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>A Paralegal makes a minimum average of <span style=\"color: #333333;\"><a style=\"color: #333333;\" href=\"http:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">$<\/a><\/span>50<a href=\"http:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #333333;\">,<\/span><\/a>550 per year. Some Salaries may depend on level of understanding, education and the geographical setting.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"paralegal-experience-requirements-paralegal-duties-and-responsibilities\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Paralegal_experience_requirements_Paralegal_Duties_and_Responsibilities\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83610277\"><\/a>Paralegal experience requirements| Paralegal Duties and Responsibilities<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Paralegals must have an excellent understanding of legal procedures and terminology. They must have good communication skills and be well versed in documentation and reporting. A successful paralegal must have a minimum of two to three years of experience. In addition, experience in office administration is very helpful for paralegal positions.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><em><strong>See also &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<\/strong><\/em><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080;\"><em><strong><a style=\"color: #800080;\" title=\"Canada Fund for Local initiatives in Nigeria\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/canada-fund-for-local-initiatives-in-nigeria\/\" rel=\"bookmark nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Canada Fund for Local initiatives in Nigeria<\/a><\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"\u00a0Paralegal Duties and Responsibilities, What does a paralegal do?, Skills and Qualification, Salary Expectations, experience Requirements. Paralegals have&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[518],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15712"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15712"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15712\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15712"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=15712"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=15712"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}